></witness></listWit></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb12438">Adam, Robert</persName><placeName ref="#pmb44400">Zistersdorf</placeName><date when="1913-05-15" n="01">15. 5. 1913</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb12438">Adam, Robert</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1913-05-13_01">Schnitzler an Adam, 13. 5. 1913</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1915-06-01_01">Adam an Schnitzler, 1. 6. 1915</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
